

[7] Setup Development Environment

    configure AWS Cloud9 environment with AWS SDK for Python Boto3


[7.1] on Cloud9 console, click Create environment, 
      give it a name:    dojoenvironment
      Next step
      Configure settings

            Create a new EC2 instance for environment (direct access)
            t2.micro (1GiB RAM + 1 vCPU)
            Ubuntu Server 18.04 LTS
            IAM role service-linked generated : AWSServiceRoleForAWSCloud9

      Next step
      Create environment


[7.2] setup 

      sudo apt-get update
      python3 --version
      sudo apt-get install python-boto3
      sudo pip install requests_aws4auth


